1
00:00:02,344 --> 00:00:07,893
We have a short time here
to come in connection

2
00:00:07,893 --> 00:00:11,383
with the jewel of human life.

3
00:00:11,593 --> 00:00:16,198
The treasure of human existence 
is to get the association

4
00:00:16,198 --> 00:00:20,314
of genuine devotees—
acyuta-gotra—

5
00:00:20,314 --> 00:00:24,405
those who are the family,
family of Kṛṣṇa;

6
00:00:24,955 --> 00:00:26,404
we want their connection.
 

7
00:00:27,394 --> 00:00:29,554
If we are so fortunate,

8
00:00:29,554 --> 00:00:32,944
brahmāṇḍa bhramite kona bhāgyavān jīva’—
[Cc: 2.19.151]

9
00:00:32,944 --> 00:00:34,524
wandering the length and breadth 
of the Universe

10
00:00:34,524 --> 00:00:37,325
to come in connection with
them and their agents—

11
00:00:37,325 --> 00:00:40,158
then we’ve got the treasure

12
00:00:40,158 --> 00:00:45,078
that can be got
from human existence.

13
00:00:45,078 --> 00:00:47,945
So as Bhakti Vinod Ṭhākur says,

14
00:00:47,945 --> 00:00:52,214
gṛhe thāko, vane thāko, 
sadā ‘hari’ bole’ ḍāko;

15
00:00:52,214 --> 00:00:53,609
Narottam Ṭhākur,

16
00:00:53,609 --> 00:00:59,000
gṛhe vā vanete thāke, 
‘hā gaurāṅga’ bale ḍāke’—

17
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,602
he’s saying,
“Whether you are in family life

18
00:01:01,602 --> 00:01:04,121
or not in family life—

19
00:01:05,491 --> 00:01:10,048
you need to hear about Kṛṣṇa,
guru, Gaurāṅga,

20
00:01:10,048 --> 00:01:11,894
glorify Gaurāṅga Mahāprabhu,

21
00:01:11,894 --> 00:01:14,826
get connection 
with Their devotees,

22
00:01:14,826 --> 00:01:18,447
and then your life 
will be perfect.

23
00:01:18,974 --> 00:01:23,614
If you’re in family life—
your family life will be perfect.

